function Start(idActor, idActorDetector)

	idAneta = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Aneta")[1]
	idVass = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "Vass")[1]
	idFireMarker = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "FireMarker")[1]
	idVassRunToLoc = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector, "VassRunToLoc")[1]

	tVillagers = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DSQ_Hawe_TheHeretic_VillagersCave")
	tAshStatues = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DSQ_Hawe_TheHeretic_AshenFiguresCave")
	tFlameMarkers = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DSQ_Hawe_TheHeretic_FlameWaveMarkers")
	tMoreFireMarkers = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DSQ_Hawe_TheHeretic_MoreFireMarkers")
	tSpawners = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DSQ_Hawe_TheHeretic_DemonSpawners")

	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idAneta, "NPC_Idle_Stand_Scared_01")
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convVassAccuse, idAneta)
	Hydra.Wait(15)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idAneta, "NPC_Scream")
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idAneta, 2.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idAneta, fxFire, true)

	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	Hydra.QActorWait(tVillagers[1], 0.15)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(tVillagers[1], "AnimKey_Cower", 0)
	Hydra.QActorWait(tVillagers[2], 0.15)
	Hydra.QActorAnim(tVillagers[2], "AnimKey_Talk_Scared")
	Hydra.QActorWait(tVillagers[3], 0.2)
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(tVillagers[3], "AnimKey_Emote_Cry", 0)
	Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idVass)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idVass, 0.1)
	Hydra.QActorAnimLoop(idVass, "AnimKey_Backpedal", 1.5)
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.QActorStopAllQueuedActions(idVass)
	Hydra.QActorFaceActor(idVass, idVassRunToLoc)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idVass, idVassRunToLoc, "NPC_Run", false)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idVass, 1)

	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorClearAnimSetOverride(idAneta, false)
	Hydra.QActorAnim(idAneta, "AnimKey_Idle_Angry")
	Hydra.Wait(0.75)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convAnetaScream, idAneta)
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	
	for i, FlameMarker in ipairs(tFlameMarkers) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(FlameMarker)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.15)
	
	for i, Villager in ipairs(tVillagers) do
		Hydra.ActorDisable(Villager)
	end
	
	for i, AshStatue in ipairs(tAshStatues) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(AshStatue)
		Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(AshStatue, "fxKit_aoe_explosion_fire_cylindrical_impact")
	end
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idAneta, "CrowdControl_StunWithIntro", 0)
	
	for i, Spawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorEnable(Spawner)
	end
	
	Hydra.Wait(0.5)
	
	Hydra.QActorPhasedAnimLoop(idAneta, "CrowdControl_Knockdown", 0)
	Hydra.ActorRemoveComplexEffectByEffectGroupSNO(idAneta, fxFire)
	--Hydra.ActorDisable(idFireMarker)
	
	Hydra.EventSend("AnetaFound")
	
end

function Start(idActorKiller, szGroup)

	Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPhaseJump(idAneta)
	--Hydra.Wait(1)
	Hydra.QActorSetAnimSetOverride(idAneta, "NPC_Base_wounded_standing_head")

end

function Start(idActorNPC, sConversation, idActorPlayer)

	--Hydra.QActorClearAnimSetOverride(idAneta)
	Hydra.QActorWait(idAneta, 1)
	Hydra.QActorMoveToLocationDynamicSpeed(idAneta, idVassRunToLoc, "NPC_Run", false)
	Hydra.Wait(1.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlaySimpleConversation(convRunAway, idAneta)
	Hydra.QActorFadeAndDelete(idAneta, 1)

end
